name: 李老师不是你老师
content: January 31, Yuncheng, Shanxi. A circus lion suddenly bit a tourist leaning against the cage during a performance. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885358495282978816/pu/img/L5wsKhIsPwimKv7E.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On January 28, a man accused Jiangsu Satellite TV of malicious editing. The man said that Jiangsu Satellite TV interviewed him, "When relatives asked him some offensive questions, how would you answer?" The man said that his answer at the time was "Maybe others will say that my affairs have nothing to do with you, but I won't say that. I will communicate with my elders in a friendly manner." As a result, Jiangsu Satellite TV edited out "My affairs have nothing to do with you" and misinterpreted the man's original intention. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885363638120439808/pu/img/N3CClKHaF9RCrX47.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: It is said online that a citizen called the duty room of Jiangxi Provincial Government and angrily denounced the local government for not taking action, saying that it was fascist Japan. The public still does not know whether Li Yixue is dead or alive. The man said that he would organize the people of the country to overthrow the provincial government, launch another Nanchang Uprising, and blow up the door of the provincial government. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885369253710495744/pu/img/ID9QPLjOjQ-5qRXh.jpg
